<plot>When the economics of life in the big city force a frustrated young writer to hole up with a nutty musician, a clash of the misfits ensues as the two artists struggle to remain productive in one another's company. When the musician's home plumbing project destroys the writer's magnum opus, the young scribe strikes back, leading to a hilarious revelation that could enable the two to live together in harmony.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?239613</url></doc>
